{
  "stem": "2074.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wouldn't give her permission to bring him and bury him around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They thought it's all a joke.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They're gonna bury the Jews like animals anyway.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Moshe Wydra, Moses like.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wydra was his last name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His family was living in a bigger city, far away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody left alive from his family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I looked after the war, didn't find them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were from Kovel, yeah, a city Kovel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's all in the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I met him in a kibbutz, by the way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in a kibbutz getting ready.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, this I have to put in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to kibbutz, because I belonged to the Zionist organization.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you had to work in that kibbutz a certain length of time before you get some papers to immigrate to Israel.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came to that kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I met my husband, he was already there a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he already deserved to get the legal-- it's-- it was called a-- a visa of some kind, a special name for it-- a paper that he can immigrate to Israel.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But he got to go to Warsaw, Poland, first and arrange the papers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we decided-- he decided to take me along on his papers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I didn't have to stay in the kibbutz that length of time in order to be eligible to go.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we traveled on a truck, military-- but different ways-- several days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we got into-- to Warsaw, Poland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we came to the big meeting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, they called us to the meeting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they said to us, you have to go back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Our Warsaw, Poland, and Lodz, Poland, was jam packed with Russian-- with German youth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were all running away from Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
